0.0.1.name: wordpress/gunner-technology-nav-bars
0.0.1.description:
The Gunner Technology Dynamic Nav plugin allows WordPress admins to create an unlimited number of Theme Locations for menus and then populate these locations with menus via widgets.

For questions, comments and feature suggestions, please go to our post: Dynamic Menus WordPress Plugin by Gunner Technology and please check out the video below.

Requires WordPress 3.0 and PHP 5.3.
